e yourself a dose of vitamin C in the morning with this vegan green smoothie. Along with kale and avocado, there's a hit of zesty lime and pineapple","thumbnail":"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/30/2020/08/kale-smoothie-b96d533.jpg","prepTime":"5 mins","skill":"easy","servings":"2","rating":"4.8","tags":["gluten-free","vegan","vegetarian"],"nutrition":{"kcal":"152","fat":"11g","saturates":"2g","carbs":"8g","sugars":"3g","fibre":"2g","protein":"4g","salt":"0.1g"},"ingredients":["2 handfuls kale","½ avocado","½ lime, juice only","large handful frozen pineapple chunks","medium-sized chunk ginger","1 tbsp cashew nuts","1 banana, optional"],"steps":[{"number":"1","text":"Put all of the ingredients into a bullet or smoothie maker, add a large splash of water and blitz. Add more water until you have the desired consistency."}],"tips":[],"recommended":[{"title":"Kale smoothie","url":"https://www.bbcgoodfood.com/recipes/kale-smoothie","image":"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/30/2020/08/kale-smoothie-b96d533.jpg"},{"title":"Peanut butter smoothie","url":"https://www.bbcgoodfood.com/recipes/peanut-butter-smoothie","image":"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/30/2021/05/Peanut-Butter-Smoothie-3430e32.jpg"}]},{"title":"Watermelon smoothie","url":"https://www.bbcgoodfood.com/recipes/watermelon-smoothie","description":"Enjoy a watermelon smoothie on a warm summer's day. Blended with banana and apple juice, this drink is packed with vitamin C","thumbnail":"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/30/2021/04/Watermelon-Smoothie-99503bb.jpg","prepTime":"10 mins","skill":"easy","servings":"1","rating":"4.8","tags":["dairy-free","egg-free","gluten-free","vegan","vegetarian"],"nutrition":{"kcal":"154","fat":"0.5g","saturates":"0.2g","carbs":"35g","sugars":"33g","fibre":"1g","protein":"2g","salt":"0.01g"},"ingredients":["150g  watermelon, peeled and chopped","1 small  banana, peeled and sliced","100ml  cold apple juice"],"steps":[{"number":"1","text":"Blitz the watermelon in a blender with the banana and apple juice until smooth."},{"number":"2","text":"Pour the smoothie into a tall glass and serve immediately."}],"tips":[],"recommended":[{"title":"Watermelon smoothie","url":"https://www.bbcgoodfood.com/recipes/watermelon-smoothie","image":"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/30/2021/04/Watermelon-Smoothie-99503bb.jpg"},{"title":"Peanut butter smoothie","url":"https://www.bbcgoodfood.com/recipes/peanut-butter-smoothie","image":"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/30/2021/05/Peanut-Butter-Smoothie-3430e32.jpg"},{"title":"Strawberry smoothie","url":"https://www.bbcgoodfood.com/recipes/strawberry-smoothie","image":"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/30/2020/08/smoothie-e080f40.jpg"},{"title":"Two-minute breakfast smoothie","url":"https://www.bbcgoodfood.com/recipes/two-minute-breakfast-smoothie","image":"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/30/2020/08/two-minute-breakfast-smoothie-4a4722d.jpg"}]},{"title":"Cherry smoothie","url":"https://www.bbcgoodfood.com/recipes/cherry-smoothie","description":"Try using frozen cherries for ease to make this vibrant smoothie. Serve on its own or with brunch. Kids will love it, too","thumbnail":"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/30/2020/08/smoothie-b9a2765.jpg","prepTime":"10 mins","skill":"easy","servings":"2-4","rating":"4.5","tags":["gluten-free","vegetarian"],"nutrition":{"kcal":"90","fat":"1g","saturates":"1g","carbs":"16g","sugars":"15g","fibre":"1g","protein":"3g","salt":"0.08g"},"ingredients":["300g frozen or fresh cherries , pitted","150g natural yogurt","1 large banana , sliced","½ tsp  vanilla extract"],"steps":[{"number":"1","text":"Tip all the ingredients into a blender and blitz until smooth. Adjust the thickness to your liking with 50-100ml cold water. Serve in four glasses or chill for up to 24 hrs, giving a good stir before serving."}],"tips":[],"recommended":[{"title":"Cherry smoothie","url":"https://www.bbcgoodfood.com/recipes/cherry-smoothie","image":"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/30/2020/08/smoothie-b9a2765.jpg"},{"title":"Peanut butter smoothie","url":"https://www.bbcgoodfood.com/recipes/peanut-butter-smoothie","image":"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/30/2021/05/Peanut-Butter-Smoothie-3430e32.jpg"},{"title":"Watermelon smoothie","url":"https://www.bbcgoodfood.com/recipes/watermelon-smoothie","image":"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/30/2021/04/Watermelon-Smoothie-99503bb.jpg"},{"title":"Strawberry smoothie","url":"https://www.bbcgoodfood.com/recipes/strawberry-smoothie","image":"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/30/2020/08/smoothie-e080f40.jpg"}]},{"title":"Coconut & banana smoothie","url":"https://www.bbcgoodfood.com/recipes/immune-boosting-smoothie","description":"This creamy smoothie is packed with nutritious ingredients. Baobab adds a tangy, sherbet flavour and is high in fibre, antioxidants and vitamin C","thumbnail":"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/30/2020/08/cropped-immune-boosting-smoothie-6c125e6.jpg","prepTime":"5 mins","skill":"easy","servings":"1","rating":"5","tags":[],"nutrition":{"kcal":"359","fat":"19g","saturates":"13g","carbs":"38g","sugars":"24g","fibre":"3g","protein":"6g","salt":"0.1g"},"ingredients":["100g coconut yogurt","3 tbsp milk of your choice (we used unsweetened almond milk)","½ tsp ground turmeric","3cm piece of fresh ginger , peeled","2 tsp baobab powder (optional)","1 small ripe banana","1 tsp honey","1 tbsp oats","juice of 0.5 a lemon"],"steps":[{"number":"1","text":"Add the coconut yogurt and milk to a high-speed blender then add the turmeric, fresh ginger and baobab powder (if using). Tip in the remaining ingredients then blend until smooth. Add ice and blitz again if you prefer a colder drink. Pour into glasses and serve."}],"tips":[{"title":"STORING YOUR SMOOTHIE","text":"Is it OK to make a smoothie the day before or should I drink it straight away? Enjoying it immediately is the healthier option as everything is fresh, but a pre-prepped smoothie is a far better choice than a muffin or croissant on the way to work. If you do make it the night before you might notice that the flavours change (depending on the ingredients), but many people prefer a slightly earthier taste. A squeeze of lemon or lime juice will help prevent oxidation and stop it going brown. Always cover or store it in a sealed jar in the fridge to preserve the nutrients as much as possible. An easier option, if you know you’re going to be short of time is to prepare the fruit and veg in advance and freeze immediately in portion-sized bags. In the morning tip the frozen ingredients into the blender with your liquid and whizz."},{"title":"MAKE IT VEGAN","text":"For a vegan option, swap the honey for a little agave nectar or maple syrup."}],"recommended":[]},{"title":"Turmeric smoothie bowl","url":"https://www.bbcgoodfood.com/recipes/turmeric-smoothie-bowl","description":"Full of warming and nourishing ingredients, this creamy breakfast bowl can be ready in just 10 minutes","thumbnail":"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/30/2020/08/turmeric-smoothie-4a1d6e9.jpg","prepTime":"10 mins","skill":"easy","servings":"2","rating":"3.9","tags":["gluten-free","vegetarian"],"nutrition":{"kcal":"291","fat":"10g","saturates":"4g","carbs":"40g","sugars":"20g","fibre":"5g","protein":"7g","salt":"0g"},"ingredients":["10cm/4in fresh turmeric , or 2 tsp ground turmeric","3 tbsp coconut milk yogurt (we used co yo), or the cream skimmed from the top of canned coconut milk","50g gluten-free oats","1 tbsp cashew butter (or a handful of cashews)","2 bananas , peeled and roughly chopped","½ tsp ground cinnamon","1 tbsp chia seeds or chopped nuts, to serve"],"steps":[{"number":"1","text":"Peel the turmeric root, if using, and grate. Put all ingredients in a blender with 600ml water and blend until smooth. Serve in a bowl with chia seeds or some chopped nuts sprinkled over."}],"tips":[],"recommended":[{"title":"Turmeric smoothie bowl","url":"https://www.bbcgoodfood.com/recipes/turmeric-smoothie-bowl","image":"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/30/2020/08/turmeric-smoothie-4a1d6e9.jpg"},{"title":"Peanut butter smoothie","url":"https://www.bbcgoodfood.com/recipes/peanut-butter-smoothie","image":"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/30/2021/05/Peanut-Butter-Smoothie-3430e32.jpg"},{"title":"Watermelon smoothie","url":"https://www.bbcgoodfood.com/recipes/watermelon-smoothie","image":"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/30/2021/04/Watermelon-Smoothie-99503bb.jpg"}]},{"title":"Green breakfast smoothie","url":"https://www.bbcgoodfood.com/recipes/green-breakfast-smoothie","description":"Blitz healthy ingredients for an energy-boosting breakfast. Using unsweetened brown rice milk fortified with calcium and vitamins makes it more nutritious","thumbnail":"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/30/2020/08/green-breakfast-smoothie-60e5e6a.jpg","prepTime":"10 mins","skill":"easy","servings":"2","rating":"3.8","tags":["vegan","vegetarian"],"nutrition":{"kcal":"243","fat":"10g","saturates":"7g","carbs":"27g","sugars":"18g","fibre":"6g","protein":"7g","salt":"0.4g"},"ingredients":["1 handful spinach (about 50g/2oz), roughly chopped","100g broccoli florets, roughly chopped","2 celery sticks","4 tbsp desiccated coconut","1 banana","300ml rice milk (good dairy alternative - we used one from rude health)","¼ tsp spirulina or 1 scoop of greens powder or vegan protein powder (optional)"],"steps":[{"number":"1","text":"Whizz 300ml water and the ingredients in a blender until smooth."}],"tips":[],"recommended":[{"title":"Green breakfast smoothie","url":"https://www.bbcgoodfood.com/recipes/green-breakfast-smoothie","image":"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/30/2020/08/green-breakfast-smoothie-60e5e6a.jpg"},{"title":"Two-minute breakfast smoothie","url":"https://www.bbcgoodfood.com/recipes/two-minute-breakfast-smoothie","image":"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/30/2020/08/two-minute-breakfast-smoothie-4a4722d.jpg"},{"title":"Peanut butter smoothie","url":"https://www.bbcgoodfood.com/recipes/peanut-butter-smoothie","image":"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/30/2021/05/Peanut-Butter-Smoothie-3430e32.jpg"},{"title":"Kale smoothie","url":"https://www.bbcgoodfood.com/recipes/kale-smoothie","image":"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/30/2020/08/kale-smoothie-b96d533.jpg"},{"title":"Watermelon smoothie","url":"https://www.bbcgoodfood.com/recipes/watermelon-smoothie","image":"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/30/2021/04/Watermelon-Smoothie-99503bb.jpg"}]},{"title":"Frozen blackberry smoothie","url":"https://www.bbcgoodfood.com/recipes/frozen-blackberry-smoothie","description":"Make this blackberry smoothie part of a festive non-alcoholic drinks menu. It's delightfully sweet and sharp, with banana, stem ginger and pomegranate juice","thumbnail":"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/30/2021/10/Frozen-blackberry-smoothie-829927b.jpg","prepTime":"10 mins","skill":"easy","servings":"1-2","rating":"0","tags":["dairy-free","egg-free","gluten-free","vegan","vegetarian"],"nutrition":{"kcal":"122","fat":"0.2g","saturates":"0g","carbs":"27g","sugars":"27g","fibre":"3g","protein":"1g","salt":"0.01g"},"ingredients":["10 frozen blackberries","½ banana (or 1 small one), sliced","1 ball of  stem ginger, from a jar","100ml pomegranate juice or red grape juice","ice","1 thyme sprig and 1 frozen blackberry, to garnish"],"steps":[{"number":"1","text":"Put all of the ingredients, apart from the garnish, in a high-speed blender with a few small ice cubes, then blend until smooth and thick."},{"number":"2","text":"Pour the smoothie into a margarita glass or a tumbler and garnish with a thyme sprig and frozen blackberry."}],"tips":[],"recommended":[{"title":"Frozen blackberry smoothie","url":"https://www.bbcgoodfood.com/recipes/frozen-blackberry-smoothie","image":"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/30/2021/10/Frozen-blackberry-smoothie-829927b.jpg"},{"title":"Peanut butter smoothie","url":"https://www.bbcgoodfood.com/recipes/peanut-butter-smoothie","image":"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/30/2021/05/Peanut-Butter-Smoothie-3430e32.jpg"}]},{"title":"Creamy mango & coconut smoothie","url":"https://www.bbcgoodfood.com/recipes/creamy-mango-coconut-smoothie","description":"This tropical shake with creamy coconut yogurt, mango and passion fruit is dairy and soya free","thumbnail":"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/30/2020/08/recipe-image-legacy-id-1243538_8-d0d9ee5.jpg","prepTime":"5 mins","skill":"easy","servings":"2 (or 1 generously)","rating":"5","tags":["vegan"],"nutrition":{"kcal":"212","fat":"11g","saturates":"7g","carbs":"22g","sugars":"19g","fibre":"3g","protein":"4g","salt":"0.11g"},"ingredients":["200ml (½ tall glass)  coconut milk (we used kara dairy free)","4 tbsp coconut milk yogurt (we used coyo)","1 banana","1 tbsp ground flaxseed, sunflower and  pumpkin seed (we used linwoods)","120g (¼ bag) frozen mango chunks","1 passion fruit , to finish (optional)"],"steps":[{"number":"1","text":"Measure all the ingredients or use a tall glass for speed – they don’t have to be exact. Put them into a blender and blitz until smooth. Pour into 1 tall glass (you’ll have enough for a top up) or two short tumblers. Cut the passion fruit in half, if using, and scrape the seeds on top."}],"tips":[],"recommended":[{"title":"Creamy mango & coconut smoothie","url":"https://www.bbcgoodfood.com/recipes/creamy-mango-coconut-smoothie","image":"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volat